<p dir="auto"><strong>Hidden (<a href="https://github.com/syntax-tree/unist#node">Node</a>)</strong> represents an abstract interface in mdast containing
<a href="https://github.com/syntax-tree/mdast#content-model">mdast content</a> that is hidden (and thus protected) from other
<a href="https://github.com/unifiedjs/unified#function-transformertree-file-next">transformers</a>.</p>
<p dir="auto">Hidden nodes are always <a href="https://github.com/syntax-tree/unist#generated">generated</a>, cannot be serialized <a href="https://github.com/syntax-tree/mdast-util-to-markdown">to markdown</a>,
and cannot be derived <a href="https://github.com/syntax-tree/mdast-util-from-markdown">from markdown</a> directly.</p>
